a2b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ar-ar.facebook.com/HKCTU/posts/1992303917476538/</a>"},{"pid":"4260f542427e13632cb965bfc52e897290246bd5","tid":1934846,"uid":131207,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T11:30:26.000Z","msg":"希望各位手足用我條link啦 搵食艱難 一齊加油<br />\n用呢條link做夠30單就可以拎$700<br />\n<br />\nI just invited you to drive with Uber. Sign up and earn up to $700 extra after completing your first 30 trips. <a href=\"https://www.uber.com/signup/drive/deliver/?invite_code=rwqfjrsyg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.uber.com%2Fsignup%2Fdrive%2Fdeliver%2F%3Finvite_code%3Drwqfjrsyg&d=wsLpXOxElywvcqXyO2fdBFSbRuvIKfaxuJHhOs3YWJk%3D&h=c9382e1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.uber.com/signup/drive/deliver/?invite_code=rwqfjrsyg</a><br />\n<br />\nCFHSHF"},{"pid":"d13b35596d4b0238a759449505a16222b96249e9","tid":1934846,"uid":17199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-05T12:28:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}